title: Let The Legends 55+ Living Sweep You Off Your Feet With a 2 BR Apt!
map_address: 570 Settlers Ridge Parkway near Hudson Rd
posting_body: ['Conveniently located near plenty of parks, dining and shops, you will always find excitement near you!', 'The Legends of Woodbury has one, two and three bedroom apartment homes with several different layouts for you to choose from.', 'These open floor plans include tall ceilings, private patios, large closets, and spacious kitchens.', 'What more could you ask for?', 'That’s not all.', 'This community has the following: underground heated parking, a 2-story clubhouse, landscaped outdoor seating area, a card and crafts room, a theater room, fitness center and a community room with a cozy fireplace.', 'Want to bring along your pet?', 'You came to the right place.', 'The Legends of Woodbury is pet-friendly and wants to make your furry friend love its’ community as well by proving them with an outdoor play area.', 'Questions?', 'Call our on-site team today to learn more about the Legends of Woodbury 55+ living apartment homes!', 'NOTE: Office Hours - By Appointment Only.', 'Community Amenities Include:', '- Kitchen Breakfast Bar or Island', '- 9 Foot Ceilings Throughout', '- Card & Crafts Room', '- Heated Underground Parking Garage', '- State-Of-The-Art Fitness Center', 'We are a pet-friendly community.', 'Dogs & cats welcome!', '*Comfortable living does not have to be high dollar.', 'The Legends of Woodbury is a community for active seniors that participates in an affordable housing program.', 'Household income & student status limitations apply: 1 Occupant: $49,320 | 2', 'Occupants: $56,340 | 3', 'Occupants: $63,360 | 4 Occupants: $70,380 | 5 Occupants: $76,020 | 6', 'Occupants: $81,660.', 'At least one household member must be at least 55 years of age.', 'To maintain the integrity of the community; credit, rental & public record background checks are conducted on all applicants.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-5:00PM', 'Call today to learn more about our community:', 'show contact info', 'Legends of Woodbury', '570 Settlers Ridge Parkway', 'Woodbury, MN, 55129', '<URL>', '*Some Restrictions May Apply.', '9lZ89Kr01']
